            "title": "WTI跌破每桶89美元 有報導稱美國加大外交努力結束伊朗戰爭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"WTI跌破每桶89美元 有報導稱美國加大外交努力結束伊朗戰爭\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"681\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6fNWx0h_V.UeQK116vuAjg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4MQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/8437bdd0-27dc-11f1-bdd5-73d31e964bdc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">WTI跌破每桶89美元 有報導稱美國加大外交努力結束伊朗戰爭</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
